Package: OpviARM
Title: Integrates ARM with Opvia
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Mark", "Lyng", , "ml@nordicmicrobes.dk", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: OpviARM contains functions that facilitate parsing and uploading of field trial data from ARM to Opvia. 
            This can be performed in R or via the package Shiny app.
